<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">如果减数接近整十、整百......，可把减数看作整十、整百......进行计算，再减去（加上）少（多）减的部分，即得其结果。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">521-98=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 521-98</Run>
    </Paragraph>
     <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=521-100+2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=421+2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=423</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>